An organisation has condemned mismanagement of children s homes. The Love for Child Association chairman Nelson Mwangi said most children in the homes lead miserable lives. Some homes are well-funded by donors and sponsors but their managers misuse the funds and other resources donated to them by well-wishers, he said. Mwangi spoke at the Liberty Children s Home in Mlolongo town on Saturday.His organisation donated beds, metal boxes, bed sheets, mattresses and food.The home has more than 50 orphans and vulnerable children.